'''Broadcap Bombs''', or more commonly known as ''Punch-and-Pops'' were used by the [[Adumari]] for their aerial bombers.

They were able to penetrate dozens of meters upon hitting the ground before detonating, which was ideal for taking out underground chambers and [[Turumme-warrens]]. A single broadcap was capable of leveling several [[City/Legends|city]] blocks.

